<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="everybody-pron">everybody <strong><em>pron</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'evribɒdi/    美 /'evribɑːdi/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>每人；人人：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The mirror never changes but everybody who looks at it sees something different. 
镜子从不变化，但每个照镜子的人都会看到不同的东西。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In a small village everyone knows everyone else.
在小村子里，人人都相识。</p></div>

<p>注: 句中常用they或he指代everybody / everyone。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Everyone has their / his duty. 
人人都有自己的职责。</p></div></div>